<s> <s> i vowed to myself i would not . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> and so , furtively , timidly , in solitude , at night , i indulged in filthy vice , with a feeling of shame which never deserted me , even at the most loathsome moments , and which at such moments nearly made me curse . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> already even then i had my underground world in my soul . </s> </s> 
