<s> <s> at other times i should have felt very much disgusted , but i was in such a mood at the time , that i actually envied the gentleman thrown out of window—and i envied him so much that i even went into the tavern and into the billiard - room . </s> </s> 
<s> <s>  - perhaps , -  i thought ,  - i' ll have a fight , too , and they' ll throw me out of window . </s> </s> 
