<s> <s> cold shivers run down my back when i think of what might have happened if i had sent it . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> and all at once i revenged myself in the simplest way , by a stroke of genius! </s> </s> 
<s> <s> a brilliant thought suddenly dawned upon me . </s> </s> 
