<s> <s> i was delighted . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> this intention seemed to me more and more practical and possible . </s> </s> 
<s> <s>  - of course i shall not really push him , -  i thought , already more good - natured in my joy . </s> </s> 
<s> <s>  - i will simply not turn aside , will run up against him , not very violently , but just shouldering each other—just as much as decency permits . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> i will push against him just as much as he pushes against me . </s> </s> 
